{"word":"ὕβριστος","slug":"ὕβριστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὕβριστος</b></el> <el>(ὕβριστος, η, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὑβρίζω'><el>ὑβρίζω</el></a>\n<p/><i>wanton, insolent, outrageous</i>: — hence <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>ὑβριστότερος</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>ὑβριστότατος</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}